As for the war on drugs. I had three really good friends in HS who sold drugs. Heck, they would have given me the shit for free if I had asked. I just didn't want to do them. I didn't do drugs not because I didn't have access (I had plenty of access) but because I did not want to do them. Making them legal wouldn't have gotten me to try them, either. I waited until I was 22 before I started smoking (how dumb can you get <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :\ --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/ohwell.gif ALT=":\"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ).<br>
